Package: WRScpp
Type: Package
Title: C++ Sub-Routines for the R Package WRS
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-12-30
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rand", "Wilcox", role = "aut"),
    person("Xiao", "He", email = "hex@usc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: C++ implementations of iterative routines for robust statistics,
    originally developed for the WRS package. Provides substantial performance
    improvements for regression estimators (Theil-Sen variants), outlier
    detection, and depth-based methods. Includes comprehensive utility library
    for robust statistical analysis.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.2),
    RcppArmadillo (>= 0.3.900.0),
    MASS (>= 7.3-27),
    scatterplot3d (>= 0.3-33),
    parallel
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
SystemRequirements: C++11
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/twobunnyrabbit/WRScpp
BugReports: https://github.com/twobunnyrabbit/WRScpp/issues
OS_type: unix
